title: Breakout Candidates and Overhyped Sleepers | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck give their favorite under-the-radar breakout candidates, debating which backups are too talented to stand on the sideline, which grizzled veterans are ready for one last ride into the sunset, and which sleepers are getting too much hype.
